image_analysis.description: A photograph of a luxurious bathroom interior. The walls and floor are covered in dark, heavily veined black marble. A white toilet is centered in the frame. To the right, there is a vanity area with several jars of cosmetic or grooming products. Above the vanity is a vertical light fixture with four round bulbs and a mirror. On the left wall, a small framed piece of art is hanging. A decorative screen or tapestry is partially visible on the far left edge.

stamps_or_markings: Bates stamp EFTA00000172 in bottom right corner

notes: The image is a Bates-stamped photograph from a legal or investigative production. The text on the cosmetic jars is partially visible but too small/blurry to transcribe with absolute certainty, though one appears to be a 'Kiehl's' product.
